SENTENCE as i said the monsoon migrated itself ,  so there was less rain in the sahara .
SENTENCE the land started to get drier ,  which in turn caused a huge decrease in the amount of vegetation ,  because vegetation doesn't grow as well in dry soil ,  right ?
